 Alpi Italiane) (1999) Studi Geografici e Geologici in Onore di Severino Belloni, pp. 525-546. , Orombelli, G. (Ed.), G. Brigati, Genova; Romanovsky, V.E., Osterkamp, T.E., Interannual variations of the thermal regime of the active layer and near surface permafrost in northern Alaska (1995) Permafrost and Periglacial Processes, 6, pp. 313-335; Smith, M.W., Microclimatic influences on ground temperatures and permafrost distribution, Mackenzie Delta (1975) Canadian Journal of Earth Science, 12, pp. 1421-1438; Wang, K., Estimation of ground surface temperatures from borehole temperature data (1992) Journal of Geophysical Research, 97 (B2), pp. 2095-2106","Mauro, G.; University of Insubria, Via J.H. Dunant 3, 21 100 Varese, Italy; email: mauro.guglielmin@uninsubria.it",,,,,,,,09218181,,GPCHE,,"English","Global Planet. Change",Conference Paper,Scopus,2-s2.0-0346361797
